#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rebuilds the KService desktop file system configuration cache"
msgstr "KService डेस्कटॉप् सञ्चिकातन्त्रविन्याससञ्चयस्य पुनर्निर्माणं करोति"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synopsis"
msgstr "सार"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> <group choice=\"opt\" rep=\"repeat"
"\"><replaceable class=\"option\">OPTIONS</replaceable></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> <group choice=\"opt\" rep=\"repeat"
"\"><replaceable class=\"option\">विकल्पाः</replaceable></group> इति"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> builds binary cache of the data stored in "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> and &MIME; type <literal role="
"\"extension\">.xml</literal> files that the KService framework uses to find "
"plugins, applications and other services."
msgstr ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</"
"literal> इत्यत्र संगृहीतदत्तांशस्य द्विचक्रीयसञ्चयं निर्माति तथा च &MIME; <literal role="
"\"extension\">.xml</literal> सञ्चिकाः टङ्कयन्तु येषां उपयोगं KService-रूपरेखा प्लगिन्स्, "
"अनुप्रयोगाः अन्यसेवाः च अन्वेष्टुं करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The KService library uses this database to efficiently provide the "
"information requested of it."
msgstr ""
"KService पुस्तकालयः अस्य दत्तांशकोशस्य उपयोगं कृत्वा तस्य अनुरोधितसूचनाः कुशलतया प्रदातुं "
"शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Users do not normally need to run this application directly; KService will "
"run it if necessary, when any of the files whose data is cached are changed."
msgstr ""
"उपयोक्तृभ्यः सामान्यतया एतत् अनुप्रयोगं प्रत्यक्षतया चालयितुं आवश्यकता नास्ति; KService "
"आवश्यके सति तत् चालयिष्यति, यदा येषां सञ्चिकानां दत्तांशः संग्रहीतः अस्ति तेषु कापि परिवर्तनं "
"भवति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "विकल्पाः"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "--global"
msgstr "--वैश्विक"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ignores any user-set files (in <varname>XDG_DATA_HOME</varname>). This is "
"currently only supported on &UNIX; systems."
msgstr ""
"कस्यापि उपयोक्तृ-समूहस्य सञ्चिकायाः (<varname>XDG_DATA_HOME</varname> इत्यत्र) "
"अवहेलनां करोति । इदं सम्प्रति केवलं &UNIX; प्रणाल्याः ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "--noincremental"
msgstr "--अवृद्धि"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Rather than using the existing cache and only updating the information that "
"has changed or been added, start with an empty cache. Ignored if <option>--"
"global</option> is set."
msgstr ""
"विद्यमानसञ्चयस्य उपयोगेन केवलं परिवर्तितां वा योजितां वा सूचनां अद्यतनीकर्तुं न अपि तु "
"रिक्तसञ्चयेन आरभत । उपेक्षितम् यदि<option value=--global> --वैश्विक</option> सेट् भवति।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "--menutest"
msgstr "-- मेनू परीक्षण"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Test the generation of the application menu database. Does not actually "
"build the cache."
msgstr "अनुप्रयोगमेनूदत्तांशकोशस्य जननस्य परीक्षणं कुर्वन्तु। वस्तुतः सञ्चयं न निर्माति ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "--testmode"
msgstr "--परीक्षाविधिः"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the QStandardPaths \"test mode\" to avoid interfering with user data. "
"This is intended for use with unit tests."
msgstr ""
"उपयोक्तृदत्तांशस्य हस्तक्षेपं परिहरितुं QStandardPaths \"test mode\" इत्यस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु "
"। एतत् एककपरीक्षाभिः सह उपयोगाय अभिप्रेतम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "--track <replaceable>menu-id</replaceable>"
msgstr "--track <प्रतिस्थापनीय>मेनू-id</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Track a menu ID for debugging."
msgstr "त्रुटिनिवारणार्थं मेनू-ID अनुसरणं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "--author"
msgstr "--लेखकः"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show author information."
msgstr "लेखकसूचना दर्शयतु।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "--license"
msgstr "--अनुज्ञापत्रम्"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show license information."
msgstr "अनुज्ञापत्रसूचना दर्शयतु।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "-h, --help"
msgstr "-ह, --सहाय"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show a brief help text."
msgstr "संक्षिप्तं सहायतापाठं दर्शयतु।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v , --version"
msgstr "-व , --संस्करणम्"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show version information."
msgstr "संस्करणसूचना दर्शयतु।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "Files"
msgstr "सञ्चिकाः"

#. Tag: filename
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "<varname>cachedir</varname>/ksycoca6_[lang]_[sha1-of-dirs]"
msgstr "<varname>cachedir</varname>/क्सायकोका6_[लङ्ग]_[शा1-ऑफ-दिर्स]"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The KService cache generated by <command>kbuildsycoca6</command>. On &UNIX; "
"systems, <varname>cachedir</varname> is typically <filename class=\"directory"
"\"><envar>XDG_CACHE_HOME</envar></filename>."
msgstr ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> द्वारा उत्पन्नं KService-सञ्चयं । &UNIX; प्रणालीषु, "
"<varname>cachedir</varname> सामान्यतया <filename class=\"directory"
"\"><envar>XDG_CACHE_HOME</envar></filename> अस्ति ।"

